                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <h2>The Risks of Neglecting Financial Security</h2>
                        <p>Ignoring your financial health can have serious repercussions. Here are some risks of neglecting financial security:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Debt Accumulation:</strong> Without proper financial planning, you may find yourself relying on credit and accumulating unmanageable debt.</li>
                            <li><strong>Stress and Anxiety:</strong> Financial instability can lead to significant stress and anxiety, affecting your overall well-being and quality of life.</li>
                            <li><strong>Missed Opportunities:</strong> Without savings or a financial plan, you might miss out on important opportunities like investments, further education, or starting a business.</li>
                        </ul>
